Class Coordinator

java.lang.Object
models.User
models.Supervisor
models.Coordinator
public class Coordinator extends Supervisor
This class is a coordinator which is a subclass of the supervisor. Coordinator inherits attributes and methods from the supervisor class. A coordinator is able to access the FYP management system.
